Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.34,0:00:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron-Arm Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hundred-thousand horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron-Arm Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-fold power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron-Arm Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prof. Ochanomizu, the new Minister of Science and Technology
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,has arrived from the USA, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will commence the new minister's press conference now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, move aside! The light's blinding, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How dare you call someone with just "hey"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the government has promulgated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the Robotic Rights, Prof. Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would please explain briefly what the Robotic Rights are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You people, don't you even care?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Robots also possess 'personality'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots stand on equal ground with humans now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Prof. Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... well, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh, piece of cake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the Professor, it was an excellent speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it just blurted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I haven't introduced yet, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My old friend, also called 'Mr. Mustachio'...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mustachio?... Strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a wonderful name, 'Ban Shunsaku'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's an elementary school teacher, but he was once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Also a judo expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Also a flower master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, his true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Shunsaku the Mustachio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Hahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Professor, the reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to fly here today is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom's school entrance, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected. You're quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Declaration of Robotic Rights guarantees
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,equal education of humans and robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen an elementary school before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where children study...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! They also play a lot of sports and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the most important of all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is to make friends with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving our Classmate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 4 people, including me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 3, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Osamu, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... 14 including me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Does this mean I have to rely on the last resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Last resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, enjoy the election speeches. Hahahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(Sit down!) (The teacher's here!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Children, Let me introduce you a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Atom, and from today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we will all study together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(How?) (Why?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom is a robot. But robots
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,are also allowed to enter the school. You all know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to study with a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(Yeah yeah!) (Don't want!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... to say... Robots are... robots...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, your desk is over there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, as I said before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because our class captain has transferred,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we will hold a new election of a class captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a class captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply, he's the boss... nope, the leader of this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will leave everything to you children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(You, who are you gonna choose?) (Well...)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we shall proceed with the class captain election.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now listen to the speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of Kenichi and Shibugaki, our candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become a class captain, first,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will purge all kinds of violence from this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you saying that I'm violent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not referring to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, I will make a baseball and a football team
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to strengthen our solidarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come come, now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I... no, if I become a class captain, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,advance the lunch time to the 2nd period...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow~~ Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...which cannot be permitted whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then instead, if I become the captain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall invite you for free to the Far East Asia's best Mechanic Circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,currently being constructed by my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(We've waited for so long!) (Good, good!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we shall proceed with the voting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in favour of Kenichi, press the green button
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in favour of Shibugaki, press the red button
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it on~! Cool! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go go! Hey, go! Hey, go~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(Go, Kenichi!) (Go go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(Go!) (Hey, go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here here here! Ah, ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just a little more! Hey, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,(Kenichi, be strong!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn... a draw, huh... It's showdown vote now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... 15 to 15
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 31 students in this class
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who didn't press the buttons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, it's you! Press it, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a chance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y...Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Kenichi is our new class captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,(Hurray!) (Congrats~)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, so you chose Kenichi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,why is it bad to choose Kenichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault I'm not the class captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by a single vote...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, I wish I was the class captain! Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish everyone would call me "Captain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your speech was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought Kenichi was much better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What now, Kenichi, since you got a vote from the robot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've decided to play up to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did a robot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,enter our school, the school of us noble humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Get the hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(That's right!) (Go away!)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher told us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That we all should get along with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell, now you're all friendly with the robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... we're in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an obvious lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, this is the specimen room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a 'wolf', an animal of family Canidae
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It grew extinct around 100 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Try pressing that button
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a three-dimensional hologram
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so real, isnt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the bones of robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Then after use...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by 'after use'?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Midori, it's for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But it's for boys only!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're not supposed to use your hands in football!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, if we lose the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get an earful from the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go fetch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No hands used...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still under construction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That why, try not to get found out, you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh, Wanna go for a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, tomorrow's runoff ballot... vote for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Runoff ballot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have another election?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Without robots, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Another election, heh heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, Mum must have taken care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to give you a word of advice, principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A-advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You should cancel the admission of the robot this instant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and rehold the class captain election.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something I've decided according to my convictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm afraid I must refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal, this school's gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who sponsored its construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The construction of the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban, my friend, about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,try to understand more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse such comprehension as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, you have to choose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It getting palsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots are artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore they are beneath humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those "beneath", are unworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Their kind should just be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you trying to say, you hysterical raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Such hurting words to an innocent child,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,only that, I can't forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by 'raccoon', you dumpy old mustache geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you should go back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... you had to make a fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding Atom's feeling, that is indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what I can't stand the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The likes of robots should just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Impudent robots...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The very fact you've dared to enter a school of humans is a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Your likes, should just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rocket Coaster", the best one here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got aerial whirls as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's no rail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't ride that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The magnetic field acts instead of the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to fasten your belt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're setting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fabulous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd round now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to shoot out to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy as a bee. Just so full of letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Atom, welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it? First day of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun? Anything happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... are mothers... always that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Not all mothers are scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are some exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Baldy, your insolence knows no place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by baldy! Identify yourself, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have you fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you have the right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,... what? Shibugaki and friends are in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do... Just what...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibugaki's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is exactly going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An instability of trance caused a massive energy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to burst in at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, the magnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is getting stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then... what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The volatile energy of the magnetic field will compress, and pile up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and exactly 19 minutes from now, this vortex of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,will penetrate through the field and explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, so to say, a Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is a person who gives birth and raises a child. A kind and noble person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes she might get angry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's only because her child is so lovely, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Mustachio Today Atom asked a great deal of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will dispatch a robotic rescue party immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Professor Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Planning to jump into the magnetic field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,3 minutes to explosion.. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What could we possibly do in this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Atom might be able to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you're the only one who can save the children now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I believe that it's possible only because it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible, even the rescue party couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And what could a small robot child possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you jump into the course, you could end up in the magnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you jump in, go around the coaster's direction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and block the coaster's speed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,then move it to the opposite course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your training in the circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Go save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Save them, our friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He jumped in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... 1 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,8... 7... 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,(So scary!) (I'm sorry!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should make Atom a father and mother
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom~!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, sorry! Ouch! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Next Episode]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm "Atom". Professor Ochanomizu said
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that he's going to make a father and mother for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy I just rushed to the Ministry of Science and Technology
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They were abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that? Who's calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You... So you're 'Atlas'!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on [Astro Boy]...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven-fold powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
